Africa Lion Advisory (ALA), a financial advisory company based in Kenya, in partnership with the Mastercard Foundation, through the training programme, Boda Boda COVID-19 Training and Awareness Campaign conducted between July and August 2021, was able to empower 3,595 boda boda operators in Uganda with information and skills to protect themselves, their customers, and communities against the spread and effects of Covid-19. Read more.  Find out more about Mastercard Foundation in Africa.